# 🪙 SabiCash Signature Mint Server

This is a lightweight Node.js/Express server that securely generates signed minting payloads using [Thirdweb's Signature Minting](https://portal.thirdweb.com/contracts/extensions/erc20signaturemintable) for the SabiCash ERC-20 token on **Polygon zkEVM Testnet**.

## 📦 Features

- Generates ERC20 signature-based mint payloads
- Uses Thirdweb SDK and secure signing with a private key
- Runs locally or can be deployed to any Node hosting platform
- Interacts with your smart contract deployed using Thirdweb

---

## 🚀 Tech Stack

- [Node.js](https://nodejs.org/)
- [Express](https://expressjs.com/)
- [Thirdweb SDK](https://portal.thirdweb.com/)
- [ethers.js](https://docs.ethers.io/)
- [Polygon zkEVM Testnet](https://wiki.polygon.technology/docs/zkEVM)

---

## 🔐 Environment Variables

Create a `.env` file in the root:

```env
PRIVATE_KEY=your_wallet_private_key
CONTRACT_ADDRESS=0xYourSabiCashContract
THIRDWEB_SECRET_KEY=your_thirdweb_secret_key

git clone 
npm install
node index.js

Request Body:

{
  "walletAddress": "0xUserWalletAddress",
  "amount": "100"
}

Response:

{
  "payload": {
    "signature": "...",
    "payload": { ... }
  }
}